Reality TV star, Tega Dominic has finally spoken on her marital status. The former BBNaija “Shine Ya Eye” housemate explained her marriage to Ajeboh Kris Lawrence crashed in 2020 before she went on the reality show. Tega made this known in a question and answer session with fans via her insta stories on Friday. “Stop hanging on the report mama T, are you still married? I will keep asking till you respond,” a fan quizzed.   My happiness is all that matters, says Oxlade     How a record label boss almost ruined my career, life, by…     Two kids of ex-girlfriend not mine, says OAP Fada Kane   Read Also: Ex-BBNaija housemates Teddy A, BamBam welcome second child The mother of one replied: “Lol. No, I am not, ended since 2020. All you know is a move that went wrong. Actually, it ended in 2020. Now y’all can get off my back, tenks.” Another very curious fan pointed out: “You said your marriage ended in 2020 but there’s a picture of you two kissing in 2021.” Responding sarcastically, the 29-year-old media personality wrote: “Na you sabi o as you no get eye, I can’t help you.”